        <initializer>2</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Pulse height is approximately 1&#160;V. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The LEMO connector may be used as input with OR function. Use short pulses to keep the probability of collision and the effect on the baseline low. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
